dcterms:description: A novel single-object geospatial tracking dataset that includes high-accuracy ground truth object locations and video data from a network of four cameras. The dataset spans multiple scenarios including an open environment and an environment with occluding structures, as well as normal and low lighting scenarios.
dcterms:title: Single-object geospatial tracking dataset
